                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18410823-1962-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18410823-1962-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18410823-1962-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18410823-cd-5" type="crimeDate">
